{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "75ef23f0-0b98-4389-b8b2-66add7ac41fe", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/75ef23f0-0b98-4389-b8b2-66add7ac41fe@1.pkg/1772597701596/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597702052", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/75ef23f0-0b98-4389-b8b2-66add7ac41fe@1.pkg/1772597701596/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597702052"}, "identifier": "75ef23f0-0b98-4389-b8b2-66add7ac41fe", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查在生活实践中认识自己。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①②③：依据教材知识，题文中同学通过劳动实践活动播种希望，收获美好，这有利于同学们在劳动实践中认识自己，更加了解自己的优势和不足，对自己的认识更加准确，故①②③说法正确；</p>\n\n<p>④：此活动与创造财富无关，故④不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选A。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p align=\"justify\">3.（改编）某校组织开展了劳动实践育人课程，学生可以体验耕种与收割，探索生物学知识，提高动手能力，同时释放学业压力。开展劳动实践育人课程，有利于学生（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">①在劳动实践中认识自己</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">②了解自己的优势和不足</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③对自己的认识更加准确</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">④为学校社会创更多财富</p>\n", "title": "3.（改编）某校组织开展了劳动实践育人课程，学生可以体验耕种与收割，探索生物学知识，提高动手能力，同时释放学业压力。开展劳动实践育人课程，有利于学生（   ）①在劳动实践中认识自己②了解自己的优势和不足③对自己的认识更加准确④为学校社会创更多财富", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/75ef23f0-0b98-4389-b8b2-66add7ac41fe@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754850778711", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns